casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 25, 2000

MERIT DOCKET

00-1544. AT&T Communications of Ohio, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 00-127-TP-COI and 83-464-TP-COI. Sua sponte, cause dismissed, the appeal being premature.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, F.E. Sweeney, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents, would deny the stay, and would grant the motion for leave to intervene of Ameritech Ohio. Resnick, J., not participating.
